Our project aims to develop a system that makes clinic appointment reservations easier and more efficient. The main goal is to save time and effort for both patients and clinic staff while reducing human errors in scheduling. The system will allow users to book, view, and manage appointments in an organized way. This project addresses the challenge of long waiting times and mistakes in traditional appointment booking methods.
